114
00:05:21,670 --> 00:05:22,900
Long time no see?

115
00:05:23,650 --> 00:05:24,830
Long time no see?

116
00:05:25,090 --> 00:05:27,430
Well, it's no wonder you feel that way.

117
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,480
