118
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,210
Three days!?

119
00:05:29,210 --> 00:05:30,740
I was asleep for three days!?

120
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:31,240
Yeah.

121
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:35,780
