126
00:05:45,770 --> 00:05:46,430
WHA-!?

127
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:48,540
Oooh! The Chikuwa Ossan! You're alive!

128
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:50,880
I-I knew you were really into that kinda shit!

129
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,300
No, everyone!

130
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:53,850
