(Right?)

161
00:07:11,010 --> 00:07:13,040
Well, we can just talk after dinner...

162
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,740
Ogei, sor.
(Okay, sure.)

163
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:17,500
Can I get some more beer here!?

164
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:18,910
We need some water over here!

165
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:22,330
