168
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:03,730
This is the Palace's esteemed bathhouse.

169
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:05,860
We're only really able to use it when it rains.

170
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:07,780
Amazing! Gorgeous, gorgeous!

171
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:08,820
I'M GONNA BE FIRST!

172
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:09,870
NO, ME!

173
00:08:11,010 --> 00:08:12,400
