177
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,970
Oi, Zoro, look at us!

178
00:08:23,970 --> 00:08:25,380
We're training!

179
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:26,420
Training, training!

180
00:08:26,420 --> 00:08:27,280
