209
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:42,180
And the Marines are probably in the harbor.

210
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:44,160
Our ship's gonna be in danger.

211
00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:51,920
Thank you.

212
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,070
Dirty old man.

213
00:09:53,070 --> 00:09:54,360
Not for that!

214
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:58,270
For this country.

215
00:10:06,010 --> 00:10:10,080
Oi, oi. You sure you should be doing that? A king doing that...

216
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:12,450
