224
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,840
Thank you.

225
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:43,580
Thank you so much.

226
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:50,750
Tonight?

227
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:51,380
Yep.

228
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,040
So we're leaving?

229
00:10:53,530 --> 00:10:56,130
Well, I think we should too.

230
00:10:56,130 --> 00:10:58,630
No reason to stick around here any longer.

231
00:10:58,630 --> 00:11:01,180
Yeah, the Marines are starting to get bolder with their approaches.

232
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:02,940
