233
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:05,200
Yosh! We're leaving after one more Arabasta banquet!

234
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,470
We're leaving NOW, numbskull!

235
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:08,180
Bake! Ba-! Ba-!

236
00:11:08,330 --> 00:11:09,790
What should we do, Igaram-san?

237
00:11:09,790 --> 00:11:11,900
We must tell them immediately!

238
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:13,510
Yes, of course...

239
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:17,090
But... this is such a disastrous event...

240
00:11:17,090 --> 00:11:19,960
I only hope they are able to leave the island safely.

241
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,750
