242
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:26,200
Roronoa Zoro, Bounty: 60,000,000 beri

243
00:11:27,330 --> 00:11:30,570
Monkey D. Luffy, Bounty: 100,000,000 beri

244
00:11:31,170 --> 00:11:32,360
Igaram-san...

245
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,590
