257
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:26,540
But...

258
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:32,610
Listen up you guys. Pirates really suck.

259
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:32,460
Marine Headquarters Private Recruit 

260
00:12:32,610 --> 00:12:34,540
Oi, oi, what're you saying?

261
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:38,420
Marine Headquarters Private Recruit 

262
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:38,270
Did you forget or something? You used to be... a pirate!

263
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:39,180
Crap!

264
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:40,890
Yeah, you're right!

265
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:42,980
Shall we dance, Baby!?

266
00:12:42,980 --> 00:12:43,470
LET'S DANCE!

267
00:12:52,190 --> 00:12:54,550
